{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"4d3b1062-686b-4da9-82c5-dfa5cb925d52","content":"No existing file found, so I'll explain the conversion directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd the `x:DataType` attribute to your `ContentPage` (or any element where bindings start), pointing to your ViewModel type:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key change:** `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` tells the XAML compiler the type of the binding source, so every `{Binding ...}` is validated at compile time.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n1. **They're on by default** — once `x:DataType` is set, any typo (e.g., `{Binding Themee}`) becomes a **build error**, not a silent runtime failure.\n\n2. **Ensure warnings-as-errors for XC binding codes** in your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <WarningsAsErrors>$(WarningsAsErrors);XC0045</WarningsAsErrors>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n   `XC0045` fires when a binding path can't be resolved against the declared `x:DataType`.\n\n3. **Opt out selectively** — if you need a dynamic binding somewhere, use `x:DataType=\"\"` on that element to disable compiled bindings locally.\n\nThis gives you IntelliSense for binding paths, compile-time safety, and a ~8× performance improvement over reflection-based bindings.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"65f82d41-36c3-4e1c-8a53-55159bd732c2","outputTokens":516,"requestId":"0823:1ED665:A3A995:BCF568:69F2A777"},"id":"36acd275-fe8b-48e0-b83d-69cdaec8687c","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:51:14.863Z","parentId":"00a589ff-914f-4303-a02e-544233bab9e6"}
